{"text": "The notion of continuous charge distribution is similar to that we adopt for continuous mass distribution in mechanics.", "fibs": ["notion"]}
{"text": "When we refer to the density of a liquid, we are referring to its macroscopic density.", "fibs": ["density"]}
{"text": "We regard it as a continuous fluid and ignore its discrete molecular constitution.", "fibs": ["regard"]}
