{"text": "In SI units, the unit of charge is coulomb.", "fibs": ["SI"]}
{"text": "The experimental value of the constant ε0 is
ε0 = 8.854 × 10–12 C2 N–1 m–2
The approximate value of k is
k = 9 × 109 N m2 C–2

