{"text": "1.2	The electrostatic force on a small sphere of charge 0.4 µC due to another small sphere of charge –0.8 µC in air is 0.2 N. (a) What is the distance between the two spheres?", "fibs": ["force"]}
{"text": "(b) What is the force on the second sphere due to the first?", "fibs": ["b"]}
{"text": "1.3	Check that the ratio ke2/G memp is dimensionless.", "fibs": ["ratio"]}
