{"text": "1.4	(a)	Explain the meaning of the statement ‘electric charge of a body is quantised’.", "fibs": ["meaning"]}
{"text": "(b)	Why can one ignore quantisation of electric charge when dealing with macroscopic i.e., large scale charges?", "fibs": ["b"]}
